。\r\n　此　致\r\n臺灣新北地方法院\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　1 　　月　　7 　　日\r\n                              檢  察  官  徐 千 雅","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c983%2c20220328%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,983,20220328,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"983","JDATE":"20220328","JTITLE":"妨害自由"}